---
title: "About Ritchie Macapinlac - Technology, Parenting, Productivity"
description: "Personal introduction and professional background of Ritchie Macapinlac. Learn about my work in technology, parenting insights, and productivity experiments."
---

<div class="page-container">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    <p class="page-description">Personal introduction and professional background</p>
  </header>

  <!-- Personal Introduction Section -->
  <section class="site-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">Personal Introduction</h2>
        <p class="intro-text">
          Hi, I'm Ritchie Macapinlac. I'm a technology professional, parent, and lifelong learner 
          who believes in thoughtful experimentation and authentic sharing. This site is my digital 
          journal—a place where I document my journey through technology, parenting, productivity, 
          and personal development.
        </p>
        <p class="intro-text">
          I believe in the power of thoughtful reflection and honest documentation. Whether I'm 
          exploring new technologies, navigating the challenges of parenting, or experimenting 
          with productivity systems, I share my experiences here in the hope that they might 
          resonate with others on similar paths.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Professional Background Section -->
  <section class="featured-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Professional Background</h2>
      <div class="featured-grid">
        <article class="featured-card">
          <div class="featured-card-content">
            <h3 class="featured-card-title">Technology & Development</h3>
            <p class="featured-card-description">
              I work in technology with a focus on software development, DevOps practices, 
              and system architecture. My experience spans from Docker containerization to 
              cloud infrastructure, always with an eye toward practical, maintainable solutions.
            </p>
            <div class="featured-card-meta">
              <span class="featured-card-status">Current Focus</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="featured-card">
          <div class="featured-card-content">
            <h3 class="featured-card-title">Productivity & Systems</h3>
            <p class="featured-card-description">
              I'm passionate about building effective systems for personal and professional 
              productivity. From time management to knowledge organization, I experiment with 
              various approaches and share what works (and what doesn't).
            </p>
            <div class="featured-card-meta">
              <span class="featured-card-status">Ongoing Experimentation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Site Content Section -->
  <section class="site-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <p class="intro-text">
          This site covers several interconnected themes that shape my thinking and work:
        </p>
        
        <div class="content-areas">
          <div class="content-area">
            <h3>Technology</h3>
            <p>Practical guides, experiments, and reflections on software development, 
            DevOps, and emerging technologies. From Docker tutorials to EV road trip 
            planning, I share hands-on experiences.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-area">
            <h3>Parenting</h3>
            <p>Honest reflections on the challenges and joys of parenting. I believe 
            in sharing both the successes and struggles, always with the goal of 
            learning and growing together.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-area">
            <h3>Productivity</h3>
            <p>Experiments with time management, knowledge systems, and workflow 
            optimization. I test various approaches and share what actually works 
            in real-world scenarios.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-area">
            <h3>Personal Development</h3>
            <p>Thoughts on learning, growth, and the intersection of work and life. 
            I believe in continuous improvement and authentic self-reflection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connection Section -->
  <section class="recent-posts">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Let's Connect</h2>
      <div class="connection-content">
        <p class="intro-text">
          I believe in the power of thoughtful conversation and meaningful connections. 
          Whether you're interested in technology, parenting, productivity, or just 
          want to share your own experiences, I'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        
        <div class="connection-methods">
          <div class="connection-method">
            <h3>Professional</h3>
            <p>For work-related discussions, collaborations, or professional networking.</p>
            <div class="connection-actions">
              <%= link_to 'View Résumé', '#', class: 'button button--primary' %>
              <%= link_to 'Contact Me', '/contact', class: 'button button--secondary' %>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="connection-method">
            <h3>Social & Community</h3>
            <p>For general discussions, content sharing, and community building.</p>
            <div class="social-links">
              <% data.socials.sites.each do |social| %>
                <a href="<%= social.url %>" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                  <span class="social-icon"><%= social.icon %></span>
                  <span class="social-name"><%= social.display_name %></span>
                </a>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Footer -->
  <footer class="page-footer">
    <div class="page-navigation">
      <%= link_to '← Back to Home', '/', class: 'button button--secondary' %>
      <%= link_to 'Browse My Writing', '/writing', class: 'button button--secondary' %>
    </div>
  </footer>
</div>

<!-- Structured Data for SEO -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Ritchie Macapinlac",
  "url": "https://macapinlac.com",
  "description": "Technology professional, parent, and lifelong learner sharing thoughts on technology, parenting, productivity, and personal development.",
  "jobTitle": "Technology Professional",
  "knowsAbout": ["Software Development", "DevOps", "Parenting", "Productivity", "Personal Development"],
  "sameAs": [<%= data.socials.sites.map { |social| "\"#{social.url}\"" }.join(', ') %>]
}
</script> 